SCOPE & STOP Hormones Analysis

10.2 SCOPE vs STOP

Fit LME models for Prolactin, HPL and GH2.

  • Outcomes: Prolactin, hPL, GH2 (all outcomes log-transformed)
  • Independent variables: Study, GA at sampling
  • Model fitted: LME model
    log(hormones) ~ Study + GA at sampling + Study:GA at sampling
    Random intercepts for Study ID and Plate
